% CI: 1.2–7.3). Interpretation This study demonstrates considerable gray and white matter pathology among individuals with LOE, which is present prior to the onset of seizures and provides important insights into the role of neurodegeneration, both of gray and white matter, and the risk of LOE. ","{16791,16792,16793,16794,485,704,16795,16796,16797,16798,16799,16800,16801,15186,14742}","156","528","{4120,4121,4122,4123,4124,4125,4126,4127,4128,4129,4130,4131,4132,4133,4134}","5"
